This file defines the scope and structure of the **MVP version of ScrollStopper**, an AI-powered tool for generating TikTok/Instagram slideshow videos from product screenshots and descriptions. The goal is to build a usable, differentiated product with a clear workflow and minimum complexity, launching July 22.

